1
00:00:43,400 --> 00:00:44,000
Xiaoxue,

2
00:00:45,080 --> 00:00:45,740
are you sure

3
00:00:48,520 --> 00:00:49,850
you want to go in with me?

4
00:00:50,480 --> 00:00:52,340
This could be a point of no return.

5
00:00:52,960 --> 00:00:54,840
Why are you being so chatty today?

6
00:00:55,640 --> 00:00:56,120
I,

7
00:00:58,160 --> 00:00:59,240
I am just worried.

8
00:00:59,920 --> 00:01:00,450
Worried.

9
00:01:00,640 --> 00:01:02,370
You risked your life to save me,

10
00:01:02,640 --> 00:01:03,480
why can't I

11
00:01:03,480 --> 00:01:04,410
give up my future

12
00:01:04,800 --> 00:01:06,260
and take a gamble with you?

13
00:01:07,880 --> 00:01:08,480
Xiaoxue.

14
00:01:08,920 --> 00:01:09,450
Let's go.

15
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:17,280
Everyone.

16
00:01:17,800 --> 00:01:19,480
Tiandao Palace acts perversely

17
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:20,760
and disregards human relations.

18
00:01:20,760 --> 00:01:22,760
We can't let them continue like this.

19
00:01:22,760 --> 00:01:23,800
We should unite

20
00:01:24,120 --> 00:01:26,180
and seek justice for the Likong Clan.

21
00:01:26,240 --> 00:01:27,760
If it's just about seeking justice,

22
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:29,280
you can go by yourself.

23
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:30,760
Why drag us into it?

24
00:01:31,440 --> 00:01:32,120
Besides,

25
00:01:32,360 --> 00:01:34,420
I don't even know anyone from Likong.

26
00:01:36,080 --> 00:01:36,880
Leader Zhang,

27
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:38,000
you can't say that.

28
00:01:38,440 --> 00:01:40,680
The Likong Clan has been imprisoned and oppressed for years.

29
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:40,920
They have already...

30
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:42,759
It's just exploiting the Likong Clan.

31
00:01:42,759 --> 00:01:44,160
It shouldn't be that serious.

32
00:01:44,160 --> 00:01:44,720
Exactly.

33
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:46,880
We don't have deep ties with the Likong Clan.

34
00:01:46,880 --> 00:01:48,539
It hasn't come to this, has it?

35
00:01:49,160 --> 00:01:49,759
Leader Xu,

36
00:01:50,080 --> 00:01:50,740
Leader Gao,

37
00:01:51,440 --> 00:01:53,360
they sacrificed a whole clan.

38
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:54,640
They're almost wiped out.

39
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:55,770
Is that not serious?

40
00:01:56,080 --> 00:01:58,080
Anyway, Tiandao Palace didn't sacrifice me.

41
00:01:58,080 --> 00:02:00,080
They are the strongest human force.

42
00:02:00,080 --> 00:02:01,920
Even if you gather all the sects,

43
00:02:02,160 --> 00:02:02,840
do you think

44
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:04,040
you can beat them?

45
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:09,160
Sect leaders,

46
00:02:09,600 --> 00:02:12,160
we are not trying to start a war with Tiandao Palace right now.

47
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:13,160
We just want to ask

48
00:02:13,160 --> 00:02:14,200
why they did this.

49
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:15,760
By uniting all sects,

50
00:02:15,760 --> 00:02:17,290
we can put pressure on them.

51
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:18,000
In the end,

52
00:02:18,079 --> 00:02:20,880
they just want to seek justice for the Likong Clan.

53
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:35,320
If we're just going for a discussion,

54
00:02:35,320 --> 00:02:35,880
I

55
00:02:35,880 --> 00:02:36,880
am willing to go with

56
00:02:36,880 --> 00:02:37,880
Young Master Wei.

57
00:02:39,920 --> 00:02:42,850
If the Likong Clan really made such a huge sacrifice,

58
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:44,880
it's only right that we

59
00:02:44,880 --> 00:02:46,120
go and ask.

60
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,240
But what if

61
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:49,720
our questioning

62
00:02:49,720 --> 00:02:50,680
leads to a fight?

63
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:51,840
Tell me,

64
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:53,280
what should we do?

65
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:56,040
Fighting the Tiandao Palace for the Likong Clan

66
00:02:56,040 --> 00:02:57,880
or getting beaten at the Tiandao Palace

67
00:02:57,880 --> 00:02:58,740
is not worth it.

68
00:03:01,880 --> 00:03:02,480
Everyone,

69
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:05,120
I just want to say one more thing.

70
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:06,200
If one day

71
00:03:06,600 --> 00:03:07,520
we

72
00:03:07,720 --> 00:03:09,120
are confined and raised like the Likong Clan

73
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:11,480
because of our own uniqueness,

74
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:12,680
then what

75
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:13,600
should we do?

76
00:03:14,480 --> 00:03:16,940
Just obediently deliver ourselves to them?

77
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,360
That's right.

78
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:22,440
Yeah.

79
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,600
I'm almost fully recovered.

80
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:45,290
Let's go.

81
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:46,960
I'll take you to find Wei Wuzhou.

82
00:04:46,960 --> 00:04:47,290
Okay.

83
00:04:58,600 --> 00:04:59,360
If...

84
00:05:02,760 --> 00:05:03,760
I mean, if...

85
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,160
After I get my revenge

86
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:05,960
and stop,

87
00:05:06,440 --> 00:05:07,640
will you stay with me?

88
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:09,280
Is he...

89
00:05:09,440 --> 00:05:11,040
confessing his feelings?

90
00:05:11,400 --> 00:05:13,240
He's asking me to stay.

91
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:14,280
I...

92
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:16,280
If the deal is done,

93
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:18,600
you don't need to stay in this world.

94
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:20,080
That's a bad idea.

95
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:21,320
Lu Danyu,

96
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:24,100
we should find a way to seal him permanently.

97
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:27,240
Do we still need to do that now?

98
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:28,600
Yiyi,

99
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:29,720
I feel

100
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:31,840
he won't harm this world.

101
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:32,880
Also,

102
00:05:33,080 --> 00:05:33,920
don't worry.

103
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,280
I won't say yes to him.

104
00:05:35,640 --> 00:05:36,360
Mom and Dad

105
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:38,159
are still waiting for me at home.

106
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,130
No need to hesitate.

107
00:05:43,640 --> 00:05:44,900
After I get my revenge,

108
00:05:44,960 --> 00:05:45,620
I will stop.

109
00:05:55,280 --> 00:05:56,120
This way.

110
00:05:56,840 --> 00:05:58,240
Sneaking up from behind,

111
00:05:58,240 --> 00:05:59,320
we have a better chance of winning.

112
00:05:59,320 --> 00:06:00,840
Sneaking in like this,

113
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:02,240
are we sure it's okay?

114
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:03,960
If we don't sneak in like this,

115
00:06:03,960 --> 00:06:05,560
do you want to attack from the front?

116
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:06,160
I...

117
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,320
Just tell me if you can beat them.

118
00:06:07,320 --> 00:06:07,800
All right.

119
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:08,520
Stop arguing.

120
00:06:08,520 --> 00:06:10,680
Aren't you afraid of drawing the attention of Tiandao Palace?

121
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:11,720
We're already here.

122
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:13,640
Are we still afraid of being discovered?

123
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:15,040
You can't put it that way.

124
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:16,960
Something's up.

125
00:06:20,320 --> 00:06:21,240
Taishu Yi.

126
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:26,240
Why is he here?

127
00:06:37,280 --> 00:06:40,240
That is the question I should be asking you all.

128
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:44,650
Although this place is hundreds of miles away from Tiandao Palace,

129
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:47,060
it is still Tiandao Palace's territory.

130
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:49,920
Why are you all here?

131
00:06:51,840 --> 00:06:52,720
This...

132
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:53,760
Well...

133
00:06:55,840 --> 00:06:56,880
We...

134
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:58,280
We...

135
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:00,600
You all

136
00:07:00,880 --> 00:07:03,280
couldn't possibly be here just for a visit.

137
00:07:05,040 --> 00:07:06,300
Palace Master Taishu.

138
00:07:06,400 --> 00:07:07,600
We came today

139
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:09,850
because we have a question for you.

140
00:07:10,280 --> 00:07:12,340
Why did you sacrifice the Likong Clan

141
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:14,980
to bring success to your Tiandao Palace?

142
00:07:16,520 --> 00:07:17,640
You mean them?

143
00:07:19,080 --> 00:07:20,740
What do you mean by sacrifice?

144
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:23,520
Everything they did

145
00:07:23,520 --> 00:07:26,320
was for the stability of the entire human race.

146
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:28,540
That's called contribution.

147
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:36,120
I, Taishu Yi, gave them this opportunity.

148
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:37,840
They should be grateful.

149
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:40,320
What a great honor this is!

150
00:07:41,520 --> 00:07:42,480
But before this,

151
00:07:42,760 --> 00:07:44,600
I didn't even know of their existence.

152
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:45,800
Your so-called honor

153
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:48,380
is just the honor of your Tiandao Palace.

154
00:07:48,640 --> 00:07:49,840
Your Tiandao Palace,

155
00:07:49,880 --> 00:07:51,840
although becoming the leader of the human race,

156
00:07:51,840 --> 00:07:53,040
has hands

157
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,970
covered in the blood of humans.

158
00:07:55,320 --> 00:07:56,680
Those who achieve great things

159
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:58,640
all have blood on their hands.

160
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:01,160
But at least their names

161
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:04,040
will remain in the history books of the human race,

162
00:08:04,760 --> 00:08:06,200
for future generations

163
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:07,800
to sing their praises.

164
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:10,820
Palace Master Taishu.

165
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:12,000
Your words,

166
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:14,180
aren't they a bit too high-sounding?

167
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:16,440
Just a phrase of singing praises

168
00:08:16,440 --> 00:08:19,520
wipes out the fact that the Likong people are nearly extinct.

169
00:08:19,520 --> 00:08:20,760
Could it be that over the years,

170
00:08:20,760 --> 00:08:22,760
what your Tiandao Palace did to them

171
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:24,040
never happened?

172
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:27,440
Their Tiandao Palace has always been like this.

173
00:08:27,440 --> 00:08:28,600
Hypocritical,

174
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:29,880
and two-faced.

175
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:32,919
Lanqi Moyuan.
